EN: Aunt's favorite food is dumplings.

ZH: 我们一家人每年都会聚在大婶家过年。
EN: Our family gathers at my aunt's house for Chinese New Year every year.

ZH: 大婶总是给我很多鼓励和支持。
EN: Aunt always gives me a lot of encouragement and support.

ZH: 大婶对每个人都特别照顾。
EN: Aunt takes special care of everyone.

ZH: 我在大婶家和堂兄堂弟们玩得非常开心。
EN: I had a great time playing with my cousins at my aunt's house.
